data.description:
Welcome to your dream home nestled in the heart of the most desirable neighborhood in town, boasting a prime location near the thriving Air Force Base.  This all brick ranch home is a true gem, exuding timeless elegance and offering a lifestyle of comfort and convenience.  

Upon arrival, you'll be captivated by the charming curb appeal of this immaculate residence.  The sturdy and low-maintenance all brick & stone front exterior ensures durability and a classic aesthetic that will stand the test of time.

The main living area of this home is where you'll create cherished memories with family and friends.  The open concept layout seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, providing perfect space for entertaining.  Natural light cascades through large windows, bathing the interior with warmth and creating an inviting ambiance.

The main floor features three bedrooms, all with large windows & great closet storage.  One of the highlights of this remarkable property is the screened-in porch that walks out to the patio where you can unwind and soak up the tranquility of the area.  

The bedrooms in this home are generously proportioned, providing comfortable and private space for each member of your household.  In addition to the three formerly mentioned bedrooms, the basement adds TWO other bedrooms to the total count (one non-conforming) + another finished space.  The ENTIRE basement is finished!  With a TRUE walkout basement.  Other notable features include a built-in basement wet bar, beautiful wood shelving in the basement, an in-ground irrigation system, security system, and so much more...

Located in the most sought-after neighborhood, this home offers an exceptional lifestyle.  With its desirable location, functional layout, and outdoor living spaces, it's the epitome of comfort and style.  Schedule your showing today and prepare to fall in love!
